## Cultural Heritage Notice

This game represents Moroccan Berber culture and 7th-century historical elements 
with respect and educational intent. The cultural elements, stories, and 
representations are created for educational and entertainment purposes while 
honoring the rich heritage of Morocco and Berber traditions.

## Asset Attribution

- Game assets created specifically for AZAMANE - Moroccan Time Capsule
- SVG graphics designed with cultural authenticity and historical accuracy
- Color palette inspired by traditional Moroccan art and desert landscapes
- Character designs respectfully represent 7th-century Berber merchant culture
